{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1f9bc3af56","title":"消灭腊子口之敌的部署","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bef26c7f07","index":0,"year":1935,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"1f9bc3af56"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b294c92ff1","type":"paragraph","text":"消灭腊子口之敌的部署！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"53664a1930","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年9月16日）彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"fdd259d6fa","type":"paragraph","text":"1.项据二师报告，腊子口之敌约一营据守未退。该处是溢路，非消灭该敌不能前进。似此，三军及军委纵队除派一个团至刀扎里接防并筑工事外，余在黑拉原地不动。我们在黑朵寺不动。各部待命出发。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"265106971f","type":"paragraph","text":"2.据夺获敌电称，杨土司有派骑兵千名来黑拉扰乱说，请注意。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"334d2803c0","type":"paragraph","text":"3.每人筹粮十一天。4.二局速侦王胡两部","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"660115d4a8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛林是","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"d01f69af7f","type":"paragraph","text":"十六日二十四时","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"8524525f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1935年9月12日，中共中央政治局在俄界召开扩大会议。会议通过《关于张国卷同志错误的决定》，指出张国意反对中央北上的战略方针，坚持向川康藏边境退却的方针是错误的。会议决定将红一方面军主力和中共中央、中革军委直属部队改编为中国工农红军陕甘支队。随后，陕甘支队逼近川甘边界的要溢腊子口。这是毛泽东和陕甘支队第一纵队司令员林彪、政治委员最荣臻给陕甘支队司令员彭德怀的电报","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"},{"id":"34071363bf","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]黑朵寺，即黑多寺，位于今甘肃省送部县东部。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56"}],"page":{"id":"ef7d081e6c","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"1f9bc3af56","start":232,"end":232}}}},"__N_SSG":true}